text: Pre-1927 Route 14 was a route in New Jersey that ran from Cape May north to Egg Harbor City, existing from 1917 to 1927. Today, it is part of the following routes: * New Jersey Route 109 * U.S. Route 9 in New Jersey * New Jersey Route 50 Category:U.S. Route 9 14 (pre-1927)
title: New Jersey Route 14 (pre-1927)
